title: New Year's Eve Celebration Party! Buffet, DJs, Noisemakers, & Free Parking!
desc: The Year 2016 Is almost upon us, how will you be celebrating New Years Eve this time around? If you haven't made plans yet, why not join us at?Ruby Lounge In Totowa NJ.?Let's party and make it a Really Great New Years Celebration! * Guarenteed Entrance To What Will Likely Be A Sold Out Event * Light Buffet & Continental Breakfast? * 2 DJs Playing The Best Of Classic Dance Hits, Top 40, And Some Latin Music * Free Parking In There Huge Lot * Noisemakers & Bead Necklaces To Party With Ruby Lounge Is Off Route 46 West, Make A Right @ The Petco Sign. Then?Go Right Again And Park To The Left Parking Lot. Then Walk Across To Ruby Lounge Entrance.
